"      Hautala T, Sironen T, Vapalahti O, et al. Hypophyseal hemorrhage and panhypopituitarism during Puumala Virus Infection: Magnetic Resonance Imaging and detection of viral antigen in the hypophysis. Clin Infect Dis 2002; 35:96.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
